---
title: "list"
description: "Lists agents matching specified criteria"
---



Validates the keyword arguments using the AgentListRequest model, constructs
the corresponding endpoint for listing agents, and returns a sequence of agent
responses.



## Parameters

<ParamField path="only_active" type="bool">
  Whether to only list active agents.
</ParamField>

<ParamField path="page_size" type="int">
  Number of agents to return per page.
</ParamField>

<ParamField path="page" type="int">
  Page number to return.
</ParamField>

<ParamField path="only_saved" type="bool">
  Whether to only list saved agents.
</ParamField>

## Returns

`Sequence`[[`AgentResponse`](/sdk-reference/misc/agentresponse)]:     A sequence of AgentResponse objects.
